use cobrador
inde on cobrador to cobaux
sele grupos
? "identificando cobradores"
set rela to cobrador into cobrador 
go top
do while !eof()
 repl cob_id with cobrador->id, reg_id with cobrador->id
 skip
endd

sele grupos
